@NODE Roz6
@TITLE "ConfigFile"


I have changed config file format since PictureMenu v2.0.
Config file for PictureMenu v1.3 is NOT compatibile with v2.0 !!!



  ENV:PicM_Workbench.prefs:
  -------------------------

PicM_WB.font	        <== name of font where the pictograms are stored 
MAGICMENU               <== shift mode (MAGICMENU/NO MAGICMENU)
COMMSEQ                 <== shift mode (COMMSEQ/NO COMMSEQ) - display new color keyboard shortcuts (RightAmigaKey) ? 
              		<== here must be one empty line
#                       <== character # if you define position in menu by coordinates (x,y) else text displayed in WB menu
1                       <== coordinate x (1-Workbench menu, 2-Window menu, 3-Icons menu, itp.)
2                       <== coordinate y (x=1 y=1-Workbench/Backdrop,x=1 y=2-Workbench/Execute Commend, itp.)
34                      <== pictogram numer (ASCII); one character = one pictogram
35                      <== pictogram numer in select position
              		<== here must be one empty line
#                       <== next menu item 
1
